ccess, wireless internet access, parking facilities  at cost, pets allowed (max. 6 Kg.), reception, restaurant, safe deposit box, outdoor swimming pool and table tennis. FROM 02/11/2008 TILL 10/04/2008 THE RESTAURANT WILL BE CLOSED, ONLY APARTMENT RENTING.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The hotel is located 150m from the beach and with direct access to one of the most beautiful coves on the Costa Brava, "La Cala de la Bella Dona", all surrounded by amazing scenery.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Apartment 1 bdrm Ocean View - The room offers amenities such as, ocean view, air conditioning, balcony/terrace, cable/satellite TV, color TV, heating, Internet access, kitchenette, refrigerator, safe in room (optional extra, available for a supplement, direct payment), stove/oven and telephone.

